      public Camp(String campName, TimeRegion region, LocalDate regCloseDate, String userGroup, String location, int totalSlots, int campCommitteeSlot, String description, Staff staff, boolean visible)
      Creates a new Camp with the given name, duration, registration deadline, user group, location, total slots, camp committee slot, description, staff in-charge and visibility.
      Parameters:
      campName - This Camp's name.
      region - This Camp's start date and end date.
      regCloseDate - This Camp's registration deadline.
      userGroup - This Camp's is open to which group(faculty) of students.
      location - This Camp's location where it will be held at.
      totalSlots - This Camp's number of total slots.
      campCommitteeSlot - This Camp's number of committee slots.
      description - This Camp's description.
      staff - This Camp's description.
      visible - This Camp's visibility.

    • generateAttendance

      public void generateAttendance(UserController userController, String filePath, int reportChoice)
      Generate attendance report for this Camp that consist of all the information of this Camp and the attendee of this Camp and the camp committee member of this Camp. Staff or camp committee members can choose if he/she want the list of attendees only or the list of camp committee members only or both attendees and camp committee members. Staff or camp committee members can choose if he/she want to generate the report in csv or txt format.
      Parameters:
      userController - Controller for User.
      filePath - The path where the report want to be generated at.
      reportChoice - Generate in csv or txt format.
